phrases.sectionDefineGeofencesHelp:
Select the control corresponding to the type of GeoFence you would like to create.

Circle Click on the map to define the center point then drag to define the radius.

Square Click to define a corner and then drag to define the opposing corner.

Polygon Click to define a starting point then click any number of times to define polygon vertices. Double click to end polygon with final edge to initial point.

GeoPass Click to define starting point then click any number of times to define pass vertices. Double click to end pass definition.
